      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <actionDate>2017-03-29</actionDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-09-11T14:02:14Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>AMBER Alert in Indian Country Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the PROTECT Act to reauthorize the AMBER Alert grant program for FY2018. </p> <p>The bill also modifies the program to: </p> <ul> <li> make Indian tribes eligible for AMBER Alert grants, </li> <li> permit the use of grant funds to integrate state or regional AMBER Alert communication plans with an Indian tribe, and</li> <li>allow the waiver of the matching funds requirement for grants awarded to Indian tribes.</li> </ul>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-03-29T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
        <item>
          <versionCode>80</versionCode>
          <actionDate>2017-09-05</actionDate>
          <actionDesc>Reported to Senate without amendment</actionDesc>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2018-02-09T19:41:06Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary has been expanded because action occurred on the measure.)</p> <p><b>AMBER Alert in Indian Country Act of 2017</b></p> <p>(Sec. 2) This bill amends the PROTECT Act to reauthorize the AMBER Alert grant program for FY2018. </p> <p>The bill also modifies the program to: </p> <ul> <li> make Indian tribes eligible for AMBER Alert grants, </li> <li> permit the use of grant funds to integrate state or regional AMBER Alert communication plans with an Indian tribe, and</li> <li>allow the waiver of the matching funds requirement for grants awarded to Indian tribes.</li> </ul> <p>(Sec. 3) The Department of Justice must submit to Congress a report evaluating the readiness, education, and training needs, technological challenges, and specific obstacles encountered by Indian tribes in the integration of state or regional AMBER Alert communication plans. </p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-09-05T14:44:18Z</updateDate>
          <name>Reported to Senate without amendment</name>
        </item>
